		   <tr><td class="headerrow" colspan="2" class="mform" valign="top" id="forumSubject">RE:  PvP Help<br clear="all" /><script type="text/javascript">document.title = document.title + ": Thread: RE:  PvP Help";</script>
		   <span class="sm">Posted @ Wed, Feb 13th 5:09 AM2002 </span><span id="notbold">| <span class="sm">IP: Logged</span> | <a href="/db/classes.html?class=4&mid=101359120095058&post=1"><a class="sm" href="/db/classes.html?class=4&mid=101359120095058&num=0&post=1&replyto=101359120095058"><img src="/shared/reply_to_thread_ico.gif" border="0" alt="Reply..." height="11" width="17" /> Reply to this</a></a>    <a name=101359120095058></a></small></td></tr>
		   <tr><td valign="top" id="fs8" class="mform" ><span id="notbold">By:</span> <a href="/db/poster.html?user=117307"><span id=>Khaldain</span></a><b><span id=></span></b><br />11 posts
		   <br /><nobr><span id="notbold">Score</span>: Excellent [4.50]</nobr><br /><br /><a href="/cgi-bin/pm.pl?action=addtolist&addname=Khaldain&type=Address" id="fs8"><img src="/shared/plus.gif" border="0" align="middle" height="9" width="9" alt="Add to address book"> Add to address book</a><br /><img src="/shared/transp.gif" width="135" border="0" height="1"></td><td valign="top" class="mform" width="100%"><p>Ok lineender, here is the situation.&nbsp;&nbsp;As a Bard I can tell you Soloing, Kiting, and DD on a Caster with Nukes is a problem, PvP or not.  Here's an advisable selection of songs to have up to Lvl. 29:<br><br>1.  Selo's Consonant Chain  <br>2.  Crission's Pixie Strike<br>3.  Chords of Dissonance<br>4.  Dennon's Disruptive Discord<br>5.  Brusco's Boastful Bellow<br>6.  Largo's Melodic Binding<br>7.  Selo's Accelerando<br>8.  Hymn of Restoration<br><br><br>Now, here is an ideal scenario (I'll use the Number of the song in the scenario.)<br><br>Root him with #1<br>Mez with #2 If it takes.  (Will interrupt casting)<br>DoT  With #3 and #4<br>Direct Damage with #5  (Interrupt casting again.)<br><br><br>Interrupt casting with either #2 or #3  at any time you need to.  Remeber if mezzed, use #3 for Direct Damage as not to break Mez.<br><br>Heal with #8<br><br>Use #7 if you neeed to run (NOTHING in the game will catch you if you have Nostrolo's Tambourine or better percussion instruments!)  <br><br>With mele thrown in, this should produce a successful outcome a greater percentage of the time.  Hope this helps some.  <br><br>Oh BTW, as a Bard, I don't think that one class is superior to another.  I honestly believe that it is ultimately the skills of the Man or Woman manning the keybord that dictates the outcome in battle.<br></p></td></td></tr><tr><td colspan="2" class="mform"><table border="0" cellspacing="0" cellpadding="0" width="100%"><tr><td id="fs8"></td></tr></table>
